The paper proposes a novel recurrent neural network model with external memory for better processing of sequential data with multiple patterns. This falls under the broad category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category as it covers the development of new machine learning models and algorithms. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as it covers research on intelligent systems, which includes machine learning. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category as it covers research on neural networks and their applications. cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are also possible categories as they cover research on natural language processing and computer vision, respectively, which are both relevant to the proposed model's applications.
